data.title: Team GB Olympians at Paris 2024: Full list of athletes
data.meta_description: A full list of the athletes representing Great Britain at the 2024 Olympic Games
data.text:
They are standing on the shoulders of giants with the United Kingdom being the only nation to be represented at every modern Olympic Games. Team GB have won a gold medal at every edition of the Summer Olympics stretching back to 1896, an unprecedented record.

This is the Paris 2024 team aiming make their own mark on the biggest stage in sport.
